pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `00d6c7d` to `bf0e388`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `00d6c7d` to `bf0e388`.
Commits
  • bf0e388 Remove Picnic's compatibility layer (#1023)
  • 17d3e0b Import BIKE Round-3 Additional code (#1013)
  • dc0a144 CMake: Do not set march or mcpu when OQS_OPT_TARGET=generic (#1017)
  • See full diff in compare view

- `update_pqclean_alg_docs.py` can be incorporated into `copy_from_upstream.py` once we're set.
